Class StreamLocalFeatureList<T extends LocalFeature<?,?>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of local feature
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<T>, Collection<T>, List<T>, LocalFeatureList<T>, Writeable, WriteableASCII, WriteableBinary, RandomisableList<T>

    public class StreamLocalFeatureList<T extends LocalFeature<?,?>>
extends AbstractStreamBackedList<T>
implements LocalFeatureList<T>
    A list of LocalFeatures backed by an input stream. The list is read-only, and can only be read in order (i.e. random access is not possible).
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
